<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ababacar Sadikh FAYE — Portfolio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #667eea;
            --secondary: #764ba2;
            --accent: #f093fb;
            --glow: rgba(102,126,234,0.3);
            --dark: #0c0c18;
            --darker: #07070f;
            --card-bg: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
            --card-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            --text: #eeeef5;
            --text-muted: #8888aa;
            --success: #43e97b;
            --code-bg: #0d1117;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            background: var(--darker);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.7;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ── CURSOR GLOW ── */
        .cursor-glow {
            pointer-events: none;
            position: fixed;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(102,126,234,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            z-index: 0;
            transition: left 0.4s ease, top 0.4s ease;
        }

        /* ── NAV ── */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            z-index: 200;
            background: rgba(7, 7, 15, 0.8);
            backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding: 0 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            height: 68px;
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            letter-spacing: -0.01em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.88em;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .nav-link:hover {
            color: var(--text);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }

        .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--primary);
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.1);
        }

        .nav-cta {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white !important;
            padding: 9px 22px !important;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85em;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
            transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s !important;
        }
        .nav-cta:hover { opacity: 0.85; transform: translateY(-1px) !important; background: unset; }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 120px 60px 80px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 70% at 60% 30%, rgba(102,126,234,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 20% 80%, rgba(118,75,162,0.15) 0%, transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse 30% 30% at 85% 70%, rgba(240,147,251,0.1) 0%, transparent 50%);
        }

        .hero-grid {
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(102,126,234,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(102,126,234,0.05) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 50px 50px;
            mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 80% at 50% 50%, black 40%, transparent 100%);
        }

        .hero-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            width: 100%;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 80px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .hero-left { max-width: 680px; }

        .hero-eyebrow {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        .eyebrow-line {
            height: 2px;
            width: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            border-radius: 1px;
        }

        .eyebrow-text {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(2.8em, 6vw, 5em);
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .hero h1 .name-line {
            display: block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--text) 30%, var(--primary) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero h1 .accent-line {
            display: block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .hero-desc {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.75;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            max-width: 520px;
        }

        .hero-btns {
            display: flex;
            gap: 14px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--secondary));
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            transition: all 0.25s;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(102,126,234,0.35);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(102,126,234,0.5);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text);
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.95em;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            border-color: rgba(102,126,234,0.4);
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.08);
        }

        /* ── AVATAR ── */
        .hero-avatar {
            position: relative;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .avatar-ring {
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            padding: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent), var(--secondary));
            animation: spin-slow 8s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes spin-slow {
            from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .avatar-inner {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--dark);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
            color: var(--primary);
            animation: spin-slow 8s linear infinite reverse;
        }

        .avatar-badge {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            right: -10px;
            background: rgba(67,233,123,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(67,233,123,0.3);
            color: var(--success);
            padding: 6px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.78em;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
        }

        .dot-green {
            width: 7px;
            height: 7px;
            background: var(--success);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%,100% { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); }
            50% { opacity:0.5; transform:scale(1.4); }
        }

        /* ── STATS ── */
        .stats-bar {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
            padding: 28px 60px;
        }

        .stats-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 0;
        }

        .stat {
            padding: 0 30px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
        .stat:first-child { padding-left: 0; }

        .stat-num {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            font-size: 0.82em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ── SECTIONS ── */
        .section {
            padding: 100px 60px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .section-tag {
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75em;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .section-tag::before {
            content: '';
            display: block;
            width: 28px;
            height: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            border-radius: 1px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: clamp(1.8em, 3.5vw, 2.8em);
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.15;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.05em;
            max-width: 520px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        /* ── EXPERTISE CARDS ── */
        .expertise-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .exp-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            cursor: default;
        }

        .exp-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .exp-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(102,126,234,0.3);
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.06);
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .exp-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

        .exp-icon {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(102,126,234,0.2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.6em;
            margin-bottom: 22px;
        }

        .exp-card h3 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.15em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .exp-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9em;
            line-height: 1.65;
        }

        /* ── SKILLS ── */
        .skills-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 14px;
        }

        .skill-item {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 18px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            transition: all 0.25s;
            cursor: default;
        }

        .skill-item:hover {
            border-color: rgba(102,126,234,0.35);
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.07);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .skill-dot {
            width: 8px;
            height: 8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* ── TUTORIAL SECTION ── */
        .tuto-section {
            padding: 80px 60px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.015);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .tuto-inner {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .tuto-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 24px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .tuto-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
            display: block;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tuto-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(102,126,234,0.4);
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
        }

        .tuto-thumb {
            height: 180px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1117 0%, #1a1a2e 100%);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .tuto-thumb::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(102,126,234,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        .tuto-thumb-icon {
            font-size: 4em;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(102,126,234,0.5));
        }

        .tuto-thumb-code {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 14px;
            left: 16px;
            right: 16px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.72em;
            color: rgba(102,126,234,0.7);
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow: hidden;
            text-overflow: ellipsis;
        }

        .tuto-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 14px;
            right: 14px;
            background: rgba(67,233,123,0.15);
            border: 1px solid rgba(67,233,123,0.3);
            color: var(--success);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.72em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .tuto-body {
            padding: 26px 28px;
        }

        .tuto-tags {
            display: flex;
            gap: 8px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }

        .tuto-tag {
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(102,126,234,0.2);
            color: var(--primary);
            padding: 3px 10px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 0.75em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .tuto-body h3 {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.15em;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .tuto-body p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.88em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .tuto-footer {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding-top: 16px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        .tuto-arrow {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .tuto-card:hover .tuto-arrow { transform: translateX(4px); }

        .tuto-coming {
            opacity: 0.5;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .coming-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 14px;
            right: 14px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.72em;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* ── CONTACT ── */
        .contact-section {
            padding: 100px 60px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 16px;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 26px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 18px;
            transition: all 0.25s;
        }

        .contact-card:hover {
            border-color: rgba(102,126,234,0.3);
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.05);
        }

        .contact-ico {
            width: 44px;
            height: 44px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background: rgba(102,126,234,0.12);
            border: 1px solid rgba(102,126,234,0.2);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .contact-info strong {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .contact-info span {
            font-size: 0.92em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ── FOOTER ── */
        footer {
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            padding: 36px 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .footer-logo {
            font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1em;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .footer-copy {
            font-size: 0.82em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        /* ── REVEAL ANIMATIONS ── */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(30px);
            transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
        }

        .reveal.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* ── DIVIDER ── */
        .full-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--card-border) 30%, var(--card-border) 70%, transparent);
        }

        /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
        @media (max-width: 900px) {
            nav { padding: 0 24px; }
            .nav-links .nav-link:not(.nav-cta):not(.active) { display: none; }
            .hero { padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
            .hero-content { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 50px; }
            .hero-avatar { display: none; }
            .stats-bar { padding: 20px 24px; }
            .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); gap: 20px; }
            .stat { border-right: none; padding: 0; }
            .section { padding: 60px 24px; }
            .expertise-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .skills-container { grid-template-columns: repeat(2,1fr); }
            .tuto-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
            .contact-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
            .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            footer { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor-glow" id="cursorGlow"></div>

<!-- ── NAV ── -->
<nav>
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">ASF</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#about" class="nav-link active">À propos</a>
        <a href="#expertise" class="nav-link">Expertise</a>
        <a href="#tutoriels" class="nav-link">Tutoriels</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="nav-link">Contact</a>
        <a href="#contact" class="nav-link nav-cta">Me contacter</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<section class="hero" id="about">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
        <div class="hero-left">
            <div class="hero-eyebrow">
                <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
                <span class="eyebrow-text">ATER · UPPA · Pau, France</span>
            </div>
            <h1>
                <span class="name-line">Ababacar</span>
                <span class="name-line">Sadikh</span>
                <span class="accent-line">FAYE</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="hero-desc">
                Attaché Temporaire d'Enseignement et de Recherche à l'Université de Pau et des Pays de l'Adour. Passionné par l'électronique, les systèmes embarqués et l'IoT — je conçois des solutions technologiques et les transmets aux ingénieurs de demain.
            </p>
            <div class="hero-btns">
                <a href="#expertise" class="btn-primary">Voir mon expertise ↓</a>
                <a href="#tutoriels" class="btn-secondary">📚 Tutoriels</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-avatar">
            <div class="avatar-ring">
                <div class="avatar-inner">ASF</div>
            </div>
            <div class="avatar-badge">
                <div class="dot-green"></div>
                Disponible
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ── STATS ── -->
<div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-inner">
        <div class="stat">
